- Ahjumma.
- Gi Dong Chane.

822
01:04:04,100 --> 01:04:05,340
To není ona.

823
01:04:05,740 --> 01:04:07,270
Je tady.

824
01:04:10,430 --> 01:04:11,590
Ahjumma.

825
01:04:16,770 --> 01:04:18,480
Ahjumma!

826
